  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Le Mottaret is offered on either a half board or all inclusive basis.</p>
<p>If you are staying on half board, a continental breakfast buffet with additional hot options is served between 7.15 - 10am.  Then an excellent five course buffet dinner with variety of options is served between 6.30 - 10pm.</p>
<p>There's an option to upgrade to "All Inclusive" where you can enjoy a buffet breakfast, lunch and après ski snacks. Unlimited wine, beer and soft and hot drinks are available in the hotel from 10am - 10pm. Then between 6 - 10pm a selection of other alcoholic drinks are available. There is also the option to have lunch in one of the hotels partner restaurants three times during the week (not including drinks).</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included. </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
