  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Le Mottaret is an excellent choice if you are looking for accommodation with ski in, ski out access in <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a>. The added bonus of this property is you can upgrade to an 'All Inclusive' board basis which includes a variety of drinks and buffet meals. </p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>Situated on the side of the piste in <a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Méribel</a> Mottaret, keen skiers can take advantage of the Hotel Mottaret's direct access into the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys</a> avoiding the busy lifts in central <a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Meribel</a> ensuring you are first on the piste to enjoy the world class skiing. The piste side terrace is attached to the refurbished and lively Café del Mott which provides lunchtime meals, après-ski entertainment plus there is a relaxed evening atmosphere in the bar. The local bus service is a 200 metre walk away making access into central Méribel easy if you're looking to explore during the day or in the evening.</p>
<h2>Excellent value </h2>
<p>The Hotel Mottaret has everything you need for a superb stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">The Three Valley</a>s. Opt for staying on a half board basis which offers you a substantial skiers breakfast and a varied buffet dinner each evening. </p>
<p>Alternatively you can add on an "All-inclusive" package which further enhances your stay with unlimited soft drinks, hot drinks, beer and wine in the hotel from 10am-10pm and between 6-10pm a selection of other alcoholic drinks are also available. This 'All inclusive' option can be pre-booked with your holiday, just pick up the All-Inclusive package if booking online.</p>
<h2>Sit back and relax </h2>
<p>The hotel has a wellness area for guest use which is perfect for chilling out after a day on the mountain. Relax in the outdoor jacuzzi on the terrace, give your muscles a rest in the sauna or hammam, or enjoy a swim in the indoor pool thanks to the hotel's recent extension.  If relaxing isn't for you, there is also a gym with a variety of equipment. Cosy up next to the<span> fireplace in the lounge area, sipping on your favourite cocktail at the bar, for a relaxing night in.</span></p>]]></description>
